Bug 11013 - Implement drag and drop of attached messages to mail folders. r=mkmelin

Allow dragging message/rfc822 type MIME attachments from the attachment
pane and dropping them directly onto a folder in the folder tree. The
attached message is fetched via NetUtil.asyncFetch with outputformat=raw,
line endings are normalized to CRLF as required by RFC 5322, and the
message is written to a temp file and imported via copyFileMessage.

Differential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D222994


